safetyTips: Delivery customers have an option to pay via a payment link, or can make a contactless payment upon delivery.
name: The Dulwich Bakery
address: 78 Park Hall Road, West Dulwich SE21 8BW
description: Family-owned, independent bakery in West Dulwich offering artisan sourdough bread, handmade sausage rolls and scotch eggs, speciality coffee and delicious sweet treats. We also have fresh yeast, flour, eggs, honey, and milk. We deliver no contact, on foot, within a 10-minute radius.
